{"tid":6231,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[洗走毒氣]如何堅持每日洗衫","createTime":"2016-11-27T08:58:17.000Z","updateTime":"2016-11-27T09:14:41.000Z","uid":1298,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d86cbe30b68234f438631955c6e9f989b73c8f38","tid":6231,"uid":1298,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T08:58:17.000Z","msg":"洗衫真係一件好撚麻煩嘅事<br />\n身邊啲friend好多都有老母/工人幫手洗<br />\n聽到我話一兩個禮拜先洗一次就<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁樣<br />\n<br />\n有冇人同我一樣會等到就快冇底褲著先洗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n到底點先可以有毅力同恆心每日洗衫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4bc8b8cbed9f08ec42474e3d8fe3cf8a592fe76","tid":6231,"uid":17307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T08:59:49.000Z","msg":"係唔想洗嘅時候諗下啲靚女聞到你陣除而行開兩步<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc6b13ab0fd6d2ab8cb2f9aab78db715515a95f4","tid":6231,"uid":129,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T09:00:27.000Z","msg":"同問<br />\n第一個禮拜好有動力<br />\n去到第二個禮拜就變左隔日<br />\n攪攪下變左得閒先洗"},{"pid":"92915da8a411087651382051576c6a5ae02c781d","tid":6231,"uid":1298,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T09:02:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係唔想洗嘅時候諗下啲靚女聞到你陣除而行開兩步<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n呢個方法幾好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n等我聽日試下有冇效"},{"pid":"79964613b759899bf8b1a4bc4835408be4671e93","tid":6231,"uid":1298,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T09:03:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>同問<br />\n第一個禮拜好有動力<br />\n去到第二個禮拜就變左隔日<br />\n攪攪下變左得閒先洗</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n巴打你堅持到一個禮拜已經好勁<br />\n我到第三日開始變左隔日<br />\n一個禮拜就玩完<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8c14a443b216418b204f11d5a3bcd3f59d26313","tid":6231,"uid":16528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T09:05:44.000Z","msg":"無底褲都唔撚洗<br />\n著完一次反轉著第二次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cef8c18fab251169b623eb457ebed6c7642bb660","tid":6231,"uid":5574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T09:07:00.000Z","msg":"關乜撚野事"},{"pid":"e9aee75235d1e7ab1c16795655bc4a6bf20137de","tid":6231,"uid":7779,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T09:12:41.000Z","msg":"日日都咁多衫開機洗 依樣至勁"},{"pid":"955c106b9caf9ab7a83237d3119d243038d2afbc","tid":6231,"uid":1298,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T09:13:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>無底褲都唔撚洗<br />\n著完一次反轉著第二次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n然後再前後掉轉著第三次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28a77b2f0963aa3f67c6b2f1787fec21f73bfd25","tid":6231,"uid":1298,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T09:14:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>關乜撚野事</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n啲人話每日洗會衛生啲<br />\n病痛都少啲喎"}]}